criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Able to practice aerobic and resistance exercise at moderate intensity;

          -  Men and women;

          -  Normotensive, pre-hypertensive or hypertensive stage 1.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Renal pathologies;

          -  Using beta blockers;

          -  History of stroke or acute myocardial infarction;

          -  Smokers.
